This paper proposes a new method for generating initial clusters for K-means-based clustering algorithms for mixed datasets. The paper focuses on improving the consistency and accuracy of clustering results, which is a common problem in machine learning and data mining. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DM (Data Mining), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
